  "mixStrategy": "Ultra-sparse, floating textures with no rhythmic pulse. Bass provides a warm low-frequency foundation (C1-C3), changing roots only every 16-32 seconds. Warm Pad chords sit in the mid register (C3-C5) with gentle jazz 7th voicings, swelling in and out like slow breathing. Electric Piano melody floats above (C4-C5) with predominantly descending motion, placing sparse chord tones that settle downward. All three layers are spectrally separated to avoid masking. Energy begins at 0.4 and gently descends to 0.2 by the end. Maximum 3-4 notes sounding simultaneously at any moment. Note onsets are staggered across tracks to avoid rhythmic coincidence, creating a weightless, drifting quality.",
